name: FAutoReimportWildcard
doc: A filter used by the auto reimport manager to explicitly include/exclude files matching the specified wildcard

Wildcard: The wildcard filter as a string. Files that match this wildcard will be included/excluded according to the bInclude member
bInclude: When true, files that match this wildcard will be included (if it doesn't fail any other filters), when false, matches will be excluded from the reimporter
